 to other\nmanufacturing (e.g., additive manufacturing) induced porosity problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Aug 2021 22:08:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Mar 2022 17:27:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 17:09:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 2 Apr 2022 03:23:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-05"}
