k-matching. The subjective\nevaluation for HySCO is significantly better (p < 0.05) than for\nBlock-Matching; TOPUP performs significantly worse than the three other\nmethods. Conclusion: Correction based on HySCO provide best results among the\nselected methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 05:41:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
